stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Queued
  Queued --> Claimed: worker lease
  Claimed --> Preparing: workspace setup
  Preparing --> Running: session restored
  Running --> WaitingApproval: policy requires user
  WaitingApproval --> Running: approval granted
  Running --> Retrying: retryable failure
  Retrying --> Running: backoff elapsed
  Running --> Paused: budget / external wait
  Paused --> Running: resume signal
  Running --> Completed: verified done
  Running --> Failed: terminal failure
  Completed --> [*]
  Failed --> [*]
